fields.product_name: Zaveri Pearls Premium Gold-Plated Necklace Set

Elegant 22K gold-plated earrings inspired by South Indian temple jewellery. Designed with a lightweight yet premium build, these earrings offer ethnic charm suitable for daily wear as well as festive occasions.
A premium sterling silver charm bracelet from Titan featuring anti-tarnish coating and interchangeable charms. Ideal for modern wearers who prefer minimalist yet elegant accessories.

A professional-grade, hand-stitched football designed for durability and superior flight control. Made using high-quality PU material with reinforced bladder for consistent rebound during training and matches.

Lightweight graphite racquet from Yonex engineered for fast swings, powerful smashes, and reduced vibration. Ideal for intermediate players seeking speed, control, and enhanced aero-frame performance.

A soft-touch volleyball made with synthetic leather panels for indoor and outdoor play. Features strong stitching, deep grip grooves, and high-air-retention bladder suitable for school, college, and training sessions.

Handcrafted premium leather wallet made from top-grain natural hide. Includes multiple card slots, currency compartments, and RFID-blocking security for modern users.

fields.product_name: Titan Classic Stainless Steel Analog Watch
fields.description: A premium stainless steel analog watch from Titan featuring a scratch-resistant mineral glass dial, water resistance, and elegant classic finish suitable for daily and formal wear.

The Wakefit ergonomic office chair is engineered with a breathable mesh backrest, height-adjustable lumbar support, and cushioned seating designed to promote healthy posture during long working hours. Equipped with a smooth 360° swivel, sturdy nylon base, and noise-free wheels for effortless movement.

This premium Sleepwell orthopedic mattress features advanced memory foam that adapts to body contours for optimal spinal alignment and pressure relief. The multi-layered construction ensures durability, comfort, and long-lasting support for individuals suffering from back pain.

fields.product_name: Home Centre Solid Wood Side Table
fields.description: A contemporary solid wood side table crafted with a smooth matte finish and sturdy construction. Ideal as a bedside table, lamp stand, or living room accessory, offering both aesthetic appeal and long-term durability.

fields.product_name: Atomic Habits by James Clear (Paperback Edition)

A smooth-writing A4-size notebook featuring 240 high-quality ruled pages, durable soft cover, and superior binding. Ideal for school, college, project notes, and everyday writing tasks.

A premium 25-piece artist sketching kit containing graphite pencils, charcoal sticks, erasers, blenders, and tools suitable for aspiring artists and professionals. Offers exceptional sketch control, shading depth, and smooth stroke response.

A mild and tear-free baby bath formula enriched with chickpea, fenugreek, and green gram extracts. Designed to keep your baby's skin soft, nourished, and thoroughly cleansed without stripping natural moisture.

fields.product_name: Mee Mee Premium Baby Diapers – Pack of 64
fields.description: Super-soft and breathable baby diapers with fast absorption, leak-lock technology, and stretchable waistband for superior comfort. Dermatologically tested and suitable for infants with sensitive skin.
A colourful interactive learning toy set that helps children develop motor skills, hand–eye coordination, and early cognitive abilities through sound, lights, shapes, and activity modules.

A durable and versatile 20kg adjustable dumbbell set featuring high-quality cast iron plates, anti-slip grip rods, and secure spinlock collars. Perfect for home workouts targeting multiple muscle groups including chest, arms, shoulders, and back.

A 6mm extra-thick yoga mat designed with textured anti-slip surface for perfect grip. Made from eco-friendly EVA material, it provides optimal cushioning for yoga, pilates, meditation, and stretching exercises.

The world’s leading whey protein supplement containing high-quality whey isolate and concentrate. Supports muscle recovery, lean muscle building, and athletic performance with fast absorption and rich flavour.

Premium-quality wheat flour made from 100% Sharbati wheat sourced from Madhya Pradesh. Known for its soft texture, rich aroma, and fluffy chapatis, this atta is processed using advanced hygienic techniques.
A strong and flavourful tea blend made using the finest Assam and Darjeeling leaves. Provides rich aroma and perfect colour, making it one of India’s most trusted household tea brands.

Pure and aromatic ghee prepared from premium-quality dairy cream. Ideal for traditional Indian cooking, sweets, frying, and Ayurvedic consumption. Known for its authentic taste and nutritional richness.

fields.product_name: Prestige Omega Deluxe Granite Cookware Set
fields.description: A durable granite-coated non-stick cookware set from Prestige offering superior heat distribution and minimal oil cooking. Includes multiple pans with scratch-resistant surface suitable for gas and induction stoves.

A premium insulated steel flask that keeps beverages hot or cold for up to 24 hours. Features double-walled vacuum insulation, rust-proof body, and leak-proof cap for everyday use and travel.

fields.product_name: NIVEA Men Deep Impact Face Wash – 100ml

Premium slim-fit denim jeans crafted from high-stretch cotton fabric for maximum comfort and flexibility. Designed with a modern tapered silhouette and classic Levi's styling suitable for everyday and casual wear.

fields.product_name: Allen Solly Premium Cotton Polo T-Shirt

fields.product_name: H&M Women Floral Printed Summer Dress
fields.description: A lightweight and stylish floral printed summer dress from H&M with a breathable fabric blend, flared design, and comfortable fit. Perfect for vacations, weekend outings, and casual summer wear.

fields.product_name: Samsung Crystal 4K Ultra HD Smart TV – 43 Inch
